How to npm install (run the projects)
-clone the repo
-cd to specific project folder (ex. cd sscgi_public_facing)
-npm install or npm install --verbose (for more detail logs)
-ng serve -o
 
If you are stack up in npm install try the following steps
-re-clone the repo
-cd to specific project folder (ex. cd sscgi_public_facing)
-npm config set strict-ssl false
-npm install or npm install --verbose (for more detail logs)
-npm config set strict-ssl true
-ng serve -o